# Harness state — .claude/state/ is a tracked snapshot: ratchet baselines
# (agent-readiness/coupling/coverage/cycle), learned-rules.md, process-rules.md,
# failures.md, iteration-log.md stay committed. Only runtime churn is ignored
# below — caches, indexes, logs, counters, and *.jsonl ledgers. All scoped to
# .claude/state/ so real project data (e.g. a data/*.jsonl fixture) is never hit.
.claude/runs/
.claude/state/archive/
.claude/state/context-cache/
.claude/state/tool-output/
.claude/state/nav-index/
.claude/state/*.jsonl
